Loved this clever, fun puzzle!  The rebus entries were well signaled and created a fun solve.   Only trouble was SAMSA/PLOSIVE crossing.  Had to whack away at the top square with lots of letters to finally get it done.  Very appropriate ending!


Great job, Mr Hasegawa!
